This paper is about evolutionary neural networks, which are a subfield of artificial intelligence and machine learning. Therefore, cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also discusses the use of learning to improve the genetic search, which falls under the category of machine learning and could be classified under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also mentions the use of fuzzy logic, which is a subfield of control engineering, and could be classified under cs.SY (Systems and Control). Finally, the paper discusses the optimization of neural networks, which could be classified under cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science).
